According to the <a href="http://www.songfacts.com/detail.php?id=20356" rel="nofollow">Rococo Songfacts</a>, in this song, Arcade Fire mock empty-headed feral, modern kids. 

 Multi-instrumentalist Regine Chassagne said: &quot;We recorded it at the church with everyone together in one room, and it spontaneously grew from a small song into something big. At one point the guitars sounded like <a href="http://www.last.fm/music/Nirvana" class="bbcode_artist">Nirvana</a>!&quot;


